{"tid":2165351,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蓋世寶試過9個月冇工開零收入 山窮水盡要賣車停用wifi：有諗過cut埋份保險","createTime":"2020-08-19T19:03:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-21T18:41:36.000Z","uid":66271,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"93c2d4260f40bc33b752246313e02b58428f178e","tid":2165351,"uid":66271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T19:03:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sNmU7JL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsNmU7JL.jpg&h=846e64a7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4ad8sJM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4ad8sJM.jpg&h=6906e1bc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n蓋世寶去年離開工作了23年的TVB，回復了自由身。日前她接受電台訪問，講到當年得知自己被調入兒童組，是因為譚玉瑛的爆騷情況嚴重，所以調蓋世寶入兒童組緩和一下，不過其實蓋世寶對這份工其實興趣不大。<br />\n<br />\n後來TVB於2015年改革兒童組，蓋世寶被調離兒童組後，試過長達9個月無工開。長時間沒有收入的關係，蓋世寶要節衣縮食，甚至曾考慮過cut保險，後來再決定賣車。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「因為車唔係必須品，所以賣咗，手機都係無限上網，所以Cut咗Wi-Fi，我本身都好少睇電視，所以屋企都冇電視。保單都想CUT但我又一把年紀，所以暫時都仲喺度。」<br />\n<br />\n蓋世寶直言不太會為事業攀附關係：「原來喺呢間公司好普遍，因為我唔去生日會、船P。我本身唔係好鍾意參與呢啲活動，感覺太有目的，唔識啲人做乜要去？加上聽聞會有本數簿，只要出席過一次呢類型嘅活動就會被點名，我唔鍾意有手尾跟。」<br />\n<br />\n至於自己是兒童節目《閃電傳真機》、《至Net小人類》及《放學ICU》的元老主持，蓋世寶直言：「當時有人叫我去casting兒童節目主持，所以我就去，但其實我係完全無興趣。」"},{"pid":"bc65779fdfc4339bc89cd299b718799433c03c8d","tid":2165351,"uid":124372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T19:06:53.000Z","msg":"細細個就睇佢"},{"pid":"d16761b95c198a65b98e33ca5fb3c9f621638e53","tid":2165351,"uid":130105,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-19T19:13:11.000Z","msg":"係咪暗示某人好多jobs係人脈，佢個腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ab91efc894b7e40c197df6e7e18da873871b671","tid":2165351,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:04:19.000Z","msg":"點會cut wifi唔cut 保險？<br />\n無wifi 比死更難受喎"},{"pid":"effb23b444696a0c3717090f13e0008dc4dcd83a","tid":2165351,"uid":201604,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:05:41.000Z","msg":"咁佢份保險幫左佢發達未？"},{"pid":"727863b54bebcdaa85820a39987280e2847d5aa9","tid":2165351,"uid":33352,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"6ab91efc894b7e40c197df6e7e18da873871b671","tid":2165351,"uid":97518,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:04:19.000Z","msg":"點會cut wifi唔cut 保險？<br />\n無wifi 比死更難受喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:07:06.000Z","msg":"有無限上網<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 文盲"},{"pid":"df68bdbfd46cf22064fe4f02ce72a439dda7565f","tid":2165351,"uid":259777,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:09:10.000Z","msg":"咁佢依家撈咩？"},{"pid":"10e24f279d78d56a08b3eeb9c727211d18624be2","tid":2165351,"uid":121546,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:12:36.000Z","msg":"我記得譚育英離開放學icu果日成班人都好開心放佢走<br />\n同譚育英做野應該幾辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc313ee534d374e41fc9ef0d5bf0530ca2a1c617","tid":2165351,"uid":41246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"「我本身都好少睇電視，所以屋企都冇電視。」<br />\n<br />\n咁即係佢冇工開攞咗屋企部電視去賣? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197bb5faf48b0bf7e12958aa8db37bb2e369aaa3","tid":2165351,"uid":255310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:18:02.000Z","msg":"係咪史上第一個比連登username燈死嘅藝人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"965896c35c906c4e1f16c3842adfaec16ca199fe","tid":2165351,"uid":32841,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:20:09.000Z","msg":"有冇辛苦到屌老母"},{"pid":"bb3d184a42910d70b84e833c8cc305d56a0b7d28","tid":2165351,"uid":38884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-20T01:29:17.000Z","msg":"生日會都唔出 出黎做野都要應酬下<img src=\"/a